border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>飞抵丽江<br />\r\n                        乘航班抵达丽江，前往小桥流水人家纳西风情的丽江古城四方街（游览时间约2小时）自由游览（赠送古维费80元/人）。古城依山傍水，玉泉河水分三岔入城， 在城内又分成无数支流，穿街绕巷，形成&ldquo;家家临溪，户户垂柳&rdquo;的高原水乡风貌，被誉为&ldquo;高原姑苏&rdquo;，&ldquo;东方威尼斯&rdquo;。（晚餐自理，大家可以在古城内自由品 尝丽江的风味小吃）。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-03 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:中甸观光或龙凤祥或同级</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>丽江－&rarr;虎跳峡（96公里，车程约1.5小时）－&rarr;香格里拉（102公里，车程约2.5小时）<br />\r\n                        早餐后（酒店自助中早），乘车前往滇西北香格里拉寻梦的第二站&mdash;&mdash;香格里拉（车程约4.5小时），途中远观长江第一湾稍作休息（时间约15分钟）。前往号 称&ldquo;世界上最深的&rdquo;的大峡谷&mdash;&mdash;虎跳峡（游览时间约2小时）。从峰顶到峡底，高差2,795.28英尺左右，整个虎跳峡全长约16公里。观毕，继续前往美 丽的香格里拉（车程约2小时），途中经过小中甸，可以感受高山草甸。前往参观香格里拉翁嘛楚卡藏药店（时间约40分钟）。晚上可自由活动或可自费参观热情 奔放的香格里拉藏民家访(自费门票150-180元/人起,表演时间约2小时),热情的藏族小伙子及小姑娘跳起热情奔放的藏族舞蹈，还能品尝酥油茶、青稞 酒等风味食品。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-04 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:丽江国际或官房大酒店</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>中甸－&rarr;普达措（22公里，车程约15分钟）－&rarr;丽江（198公里，车程约3.5小时）<br />\r\n                        早餐后（酒店自助中早），远观参观藏族民居（游览时间约15分钟）。之后前往游览普达措国家森林公园（含景区内观光环保车。游览时间约3-4小时）游览属 都湖、香格里拉文化村,前往碧塔海，碧塔海位于中甸县城东25公里的高山峻岭中，它由雪山溪流汇聚而成，湖水碧蓝，雪山树影倒映湖中，清丽醉人，湖中有 岛，生长着云杉、高山松、高山栎、白桦、柳等。湖四周生长着浓密的杜鹃花林，每年杜鹃花开的季节，花瓣落入湖水，被鱼误食，不时一条条被醉倒，白色鱼肚皮 飘浮在杜鹃花之中，随波荡漾，形成&ldquo;杜鹃醉鱼&rdquo;的奇观。之后乘车返回丽江，晚餐后，入住酒店。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-05 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:丽江国际或官房大酒店</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>丽江－&rarr;玉龙雪山（20公里，车程约30分钟）－&rarr;玉水寨&mdash;&mdash;束河古镇<br />\r\n                        早餐后（酒店自助中早），前往横断山脉之南的滇西北高原上的被誉称为东方阿尔卑斯山的绿色雪峰&mdash;&mdash;玉龙雪山（除排队乘坐缆车外，游览时间约1小时）（此天 行程为景点套票，若因客人自身原因不去游览，费用不退）团友可自费乘小索道云杉坪上山（索道费57元、环保车20元自理），小索道位于玉龙雪山东麓的山箐 里，在雪山主峰的右下方。15分钟的空中索道即可到达云杉坪。（注：因玉龙雪山海拔较高，因个人体质不同，可能会有高原反应，所以我社不集体安排索道游 览，请各位团友依据个人身体情况自由选择。有高血压、心脏病等疾病病历者和孕妇、幼儿、年老体弱者不宜参加高海拔行程，索道的下部设有医疗站）之后游览位 于玉龙雪山东麓的甘海子，游白水河（游览时间约20分钟，不含环保车50元/人）。之后可自费欣赏张艺谋导演的《印象丽江》（门票费用自理190元/人， 表演时间约90分钟）。看完表演后，前往游览玉水寨（游览时间约40分钟）。前往参观丽江滇缅珠宝店（时间约40分钟）。之后前往张艺谋《千里走单骑》拍 摄基地、世界文化遗产&mdash;&mdash;束河古镇（游览时间约1.5小时），它是茶马古道上保存完好的重要集镇，也是纳西先民从农耕文明向商业文明过度的活标本，是对外 开放和马帮活动形成的集镇建设典范，您可在这里体验茶马文化&hellip;&hellip;夜幕降临，可以在古镇内幽静的小巷里泡吧。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-06 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>丽江－&rarr;机场（40公里，车程约40分钟）<br />\r\n                        早餐后，丽江古城自由活动，再次流连丽江古城的柔软时光，为您的亲朋挑选喜欢的礼物，午餐后，乘机返回程。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>', '', 1, 1, '', '2012-04-05', '2012-04-05 17:04:49', '2012-04-20 10:44:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);
