style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>『杭州――三亚』乘机飞抵三亚，专人机场接机，送达酒店，酒店大堂专人为客人办理入住手续。 （三亚凤凰机场接机电话：13322099207）</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="98" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 73.3pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-21 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="311" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 232.9pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:三亚南田好汉坡凯莱温泉度假酒店<br />\r\n            或兴隆老榕树/康乐园同级温泉度假酒店）</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="117" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 87.6pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>『三亚――南田/兴隆』<br />\r\n                        早餐后赴蔚蓝大海中一座苍翠岛屿、人称情人岛的&mdash;&mdash;【蜈支州岛】看海，眺山海奇观，觅心<br />\r\n                        灵归隐（游览时间180分种，含上下岛时间），赴海南热带香巴拉&mdash;&mdash;【呀诺达雨林文化旅游区】，<br />\r\n                        享用&ldquo;雨林药膳&rdquo;（VTP围桌），餐后欣赏海南独特的热带雨林景观，体会空中天道的震撼和新奇<br />\r\n                        （赠含40元/人景区观光车）（游览时间150分钟）；赴兴隆或南田，晚餐品尝温泉或农家乐风味<br />\r\n                        餐。晚间尽享海岛地热温泉鱼疗之惬意（费用均需另付）。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="98" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 73.3pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-22 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="311" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 232.9pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:三亚湾假日(或明申锦江雅致房/国光豪生休闲房/山海天园景房/阳光大酒店园景房）</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="117" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 87.6pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>『南田/兴隆――三亚』<br />\r\n                        早餐后出发赴海南省游客满意十佳景区和十大最佳特色魅力旅游风景区之一，被誉为省内&ldquo;最丰富、最权威、最灵动、最纯正的民族文化&ldquo;活体&rdquo;博物馆&rdquo;&mdash;【槟榔 谷原著民文华村】，体验海南多彩文化，观大型实景民俗演艺（游览时间约2.5小时），午餐后赴&ldquo;东方夏威夷&rdquo;【亚龙湾中心广场,贝壳馆、沙滩】，在海南岛 最美的海域体验各种丰富多彩的海上娱乐项目（潜水需另付费，游览时间150分钟）；返回三亚，赴三亚免税店，了解世界名品，尽享国人离岛免税政策（游览时 间约70分钟）。晚餐品尝地道晚间推荐海鲜风味套餐：椰子盅、龙虾、对虾、石斑鱼、鲍鱼、糕蟹、鱼肚汤、海胆、海鳗、海参、贝类、四大名菜等合计20多个 品种，可谓饕餮盛宴（费用180元/人需另付）。晚餐后可欣赏异国风情表演（费用200元/人需另付费）。提示：不喜欢海鲜风味餐的客人，旅行社会提供 350元/桌10人用的8菜1汤品质晚餐或按标准退费均可。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="98" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 73.3pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-23 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="311" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 232.9pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:三亚湾假日(或明申锦江雅致房/国光豪生休闲房/山海天园景房/阳光大酒店园景房）</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="117" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 87.6pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>『三亚』<br />\r\n                        早餐后出发，赴福泽之地&mdash;&mdash;【南山文化旅游区】，深度体验南山生态文化、园林文化、福寿文化等，并零距离观世界上最高的南山海上观音圣像（游览时间150 分钟），指定南山私房菜菜馆品尝南山素斋，下午游览&ldquo;海天一色&rdquo;的【天涯海角】，在夕阳下拍摄天涯感动，感受人在天涯的潇洒与浪漫（游览时间150分 钟）。晚间可乘&ldquo;逍遥号&rdquo;豪华游轮夜游三亚湾，体验海上狂欢之乐趣（费用268元/人需另付，含啤酒、饮料、快乐演艺。船上烧烤食品需另付费）。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="98" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 73.3pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-24 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="311" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 232.9pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:『返回温暖的家』</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="117" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 87.6pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>『三亚――杭州』<br />\r\n                        早送机，或者早餐后，自由活动，12：00前退房，根据各自航班送机（三亚凤凰机场送机电话：189762685990）；</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 1, '', '2012-04-19', '2012-04-19 11:37:52', '2012-04-20 17:30:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);
