dy>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>杭州萧山机场乘飞机飞往桂林，桂林两江国际机场接团,入住酒店。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-03 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:桂林(帝苑大酒店)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm" colspan="3">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>早餐后游览半枕漓江---伏波山公园（约40分钟）。乘船游览有东方威尼斯之称的桂林水上公 园&mdash;&mdash;四湖景区（约1小时），(中国古典园林&mdash;榕杉湖景区,天人合一的生态园林&mdash;桂湖景区,宋历史文化园&mdash;木龙湖景区),沿途观赏景区内新建成的名桥博览 园,名花名树博览园,亭台楼阁博览园和雕塑博览园;榕湖观看音乐喷泉。可乘车游览古东森林景区(约1.5小时)(费用自理，120元/人)，那里有中央电 视台报道的：可以触摸的瀑布，让您换种方式游玩的&ldquo;走瀑戏浪&rdquo;；观千亩枫林，走200米的空悬吊桥；入幽静山林、观百鸟齐鸣。或游览冠岩景区（约1.5小 时）（费用自理,140元/人），冠岩是游览方式最多、平地滑道最长而得名，它是唯一集海、陆、空为一体的立体式岩洞，乘车前往游览义江缘景区(游览约 2.5小时):在这里可以领略临桂八景之首的&ldquo;义江风光&rdquo;,还可以和壮族歌仙对歌，聆听&ldquo;侗族大歌&rdquo;的天籁之音、感受白裤瑶族长发的奇特风俗，又可游览义 江两岸少数民族的各种风情、建筑景观。义江缘民艺走廊的数十种各类少数民族传统手工技艺同样能使你目不暇接。晚餐享用用侗家长廊宴,在敬酒歌声中畅饮侗家 米酒。晚上观看原滋原味的少数民族歌舞表演（18：30开演），并可以身临其境的参于狂欢！</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-04 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:阳朔(唐人街或同级)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中,晚</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm" colspan="3">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>早餐后乘船游览最具诗情画意的百里画廊&mdash;&mdash;漓江风光（竹江-阳朔）(约4.5小时)；自由闲 逛中国三大洋人街之一的阳朔西街（约1小时）。可乘车前往游览以音乐石屏、广寒深宫、雪山飞瀑&ldquo;三绝&rdquo;和佛祖论经、独柱擎天、混元珍珠伞&ldquo;三宝&rdquo;等景点为 代表，栩栩如生、形象逼真的&ldquo;世界岩溶奇观&rdquo;银子岩（约1小时）(费用自理,110元/人)。晚餐后可观赏张艺谋导演的大型山水实景表演---印象刘三姐 （约70分钟）(费用自理,220元/人或260元/人)。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>04-05 行程</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="429" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 321.75pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>住:</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="150" style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 112.5pt; padding-right: 0cm; background: #efefef; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n            <div>餐:早,中</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n            <td style="border-bottom: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-left: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; border-right: #cfcfcf 1pt inset; padding-top: 0cm" colspan="3">\r\n            <div align="center">\r\n            <table width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 95%">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style="height: 18.75pt">\r\n                        <td style="border-bottom: #f0f0f0; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 0cm; height: 18.75pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; padding-top: 0cm">\r\n                        <div>早餐后乘车返桂林，前往一个比桃花源更美、更真实的地方--【世外桃源】（约1.5小时、门 票自理,100元/人），让您走进陶渊明《桃花源记》中的人间圣地，游毕沿着桂花之路返回桂林。游览桂林城徽&mdash;－象鼻山（约1小时）。游览具有600多年 的历史的【靖江王府】&rdquo;，南天一柱&rdquo;&mdash;【独秀峰】(游览时间约50分钟)。乘飞机返回杭州。</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '', 1, 1, '', '2012-04-20', '2012-04-20 10:48:38', '2012-04-20 10:53:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);

